  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0d87\u0db8\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A certificate from the Minister regarding rice",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mahinda Amaraweera, Minister of Agriculture, Wildlife and Forest Conservation said that the price of rice is likely to come down further in the future.",
        "Paddy is being harvested in Vavuniya, Mullaitivu and Ampara and will be available in the near future, the Minister said.",
        "The Minister of Agriculture said that the Paddy Marketing Board has been instructed to prepare for the purchase of paddy during the Yala season. There will be no shortage of rice in the country in the near future, he said.",
        "This was stated by the Minister of Agriculture at the opening of the \"PMB Rice\" rice outlet at the Ministry of Agriculture premises today (27).",
        "A Milco product outlet and a mobile outlet for the National Livestock Development Board's coconut, coconut oil and milk products outlets were opened at the same premises today.",
        "Secretary to the Ministry of Agriculture Rohana Pushpakumara, Chairman of the Paddy Marketing Board Neil de Alwis and Chairman of Milco Renuka Perera were also present."
      ],
